helper.subset26.tables

Class GenericTable

  • java.lang.Object
    • helper.subset26.tables.GenericTable
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    AbbreviationsTable, AcknowledgementTable, ConditionTable, ConditionTableWArrows, DataListTable, FieldListTable, FieldTable, FieldTableWSpecialValues, FunctionsTable, GeneralFormatTable, LevelInformationTable, LevelInformationTwoNTCTable, MessageActionTable, MessageListTable, ModesDataTable, ModesTable, ModesTable2, PacketFieldsTable, PacketReferenceTable, Procedures2ColumnTable, Procedures3Column1BlankTable, Procedures3ColumnTable, TermTable, TrainCommandTable, TransitionTable, TransitionTableWArrows, TransitionTableWArrowsNarrow, VersionHistoryTableNarrow, VersionHistoryTableWide

    abstract class GenericTable
extends java.lang.Object
    Match known patterns of tables (i.e. abstract descriptions of how they look like) with those found in the subset-026 and use this data to add proper traceability links
    Author:
    Moritz Dorka
